---
title: Carb Smart Tex-Mex Beyond Meat® Stew with Sour Cream and Tortilla Crumble
description: Inspired by Tex-Mex tacos, this comforting stew is perfect for the carb-conscious eater. Savoury and lightly spiced Beyond Meat® stew is a delicious base for a fully loaded topping experience of crispy tortillas and elote inspired corn.

